CC ->> CC: Calculate Charge

CC ->> SBAPI: POST /agreements/due-diligence
note left
{
    "payer": {
            "partyIdType": "ACCOUNT_NUMBER",
            "partyIdentifier": "10086784563219",
            "dfspId": "STANBANK_MW",
